1
00:00:10,960 --> 00:00:13,420
♪The maple mark on your skin♪

2
00:00:14,230 --> 00:00:17,040
♪The only proof we exist♪

3
00:00:18,210 --> 00:00:21,450
♪I stole you back from destiny♪

4
00:00:21,560 --> 00:00:24,430
♪But can I redeem myself♪

5
00:00:24,430 --> 00:00:26,540
♪I don't care what fate foretells♪

6
00:00:26,750 --> 00:00:30,330
♪Or how rough the road may be♪

7
00:00:30,340 --> 00:00:33,280
♪Stay, I'll fight for you♪

8
00:00:33,610 --> 00:00:37,660
♪That's all I'll ever do♪

9
00:00:37,760 --> 00:00:39,890
♪If life is just a show♪

10
00:00:39,890 --> 00:00:42,650
♪I'll stay with you till the end♪

11
00:00:42,650 --> 00:00:44,980
♪I'm scared we'll wake up alone♪

12
00:00:44,980 --> 00:00:47,960
♪So don't let this dream end♪

13
00:00:47,960 --> 00:00:52,420
♪In my bones, in my heart♪

14
00:00:52,420 --> 00:00:54,100
♪I know I'll have to leave♪

15
00:00:54,100 --> 00:00:55,670
♪You must not leave my side♪

16
00:00:55,670 --> 00:00:57,260
♪No place can hold us in♪

17
00:00:57,260 --> 00:01:01,910
♪Not when it's you and me♪

18
00:01:06,890 --> 00:01:10,400
♪Forever♪

19
00:01:11,490 --> 00:01:15,250
♪In my soul♪

20
00:01:17,260 --> 00:01:23,300
=This Palace Maid Isn't Very Calm=
=Episode 24=

21
00:01:25,400 --> 00:01:26,430
All this time,

22
00:01:26,590 --> 00:01:28,350
you've endured so much for me.

23
00:01:29,000 --> 00:01:30,350
And now because of me,

24
00:01:30,590 --> 00:01:32,840
you missed your chance
with the 14th Prince.

25
00:01:33,200 --> 00:01:36,640
I owe you more than
I can repay in this life.

26
00:01:38,640 --> 00:01:40,120
This has nothing to do with you.

27
00:01:40,510 --> 00:01:41,950
Since I promised you,

28
00:01:42,000 --> 00:01:43,640
you just need to rest
and carry the baby safely.

29
00:01:44,230 --> 00:01:46,790
Giving birth safely.

30
00:01:46,950 --> 00:01:48,480
That is what matters most.

31
00:01:55,150 --> 00:01:57,000
Greetings, Concubine Hui.

32
00:01:57,350 --> 00:01:58,480
Consort Lan

33
00:01:58,480 --> 00:02:00,350
wants the pastries made by Miss Ye Jin.

34
00:02:00,400 --> 00:02:02,400
Miss Ye Jin, please come with us.

35
00:02:05,150 --> 00:02:06,790
I'm unwell today.

36
00:02:06,950 --> 00:02:08,030
I'm afraid I cannot come.

37
00:02:08,240 --> 00:02:09,840
I ask Consort Lan for forgiveness.

38
00:02:09,910 --> 00:02:12,190
Consort Lan is with child.

39
00:02:12,360 --> 00:02:14,000
She has no appetite these days.

40
00:02:14,030 --> 00:02:16,030
She finally craves something to eat.

41
00:02:16,710 --> 00:02:18,910
Please don't refuse, Miss Ye Jin.

42
00:02:20,750 --> 00:02:22,560
Ye Jin is really unwell.

43
00:02:22,960 --> 00:02:25,400
Miss Cuiwei, why press her so hard?

44
00:02:26,910 --> 00:02:28,520
Ye Jin, let's go.

45
00:02:37,240 --> 00:02:39,400
Protecting Concubine Hui is your duty.

46
00:02:39,430 --> 00:02:41,400
But this has nothing to do with her.

47
00:02:41,840 --> 00:02:43,840
Ye Jin is just a lowly maid.

48
00:02:44,000 --> 00:02:46,000
You dare defy Consort Lan's order.

49
00:02:46,520 --> 00:02:48,120
Are you really going to

50
00:02:48,120 --> 00:02:49,750
offend Consort Lan for her sake?

51
00:02:51,190 --> 00:02:52,030
You...

52
00:02:52,840 --> 00:02:55,400
Concubine Hui, best not meddle in this.

53
00:02:55,840 --> 00:02:58,400
His Majesty went to the suburban camp
early today.

54
00:02:58,750 --> 00:03:00,910
No one in the palace
can protect you now.

55
00:03:01,630 --> 00:03:02,910
With your strength alone,

56
00:03:03,360 --> 00:03:05,840
how can you defy Consort Lan?

57
00:03:07,190 --> 00:03:08,030
Guards.

58
00:03:08,400 --> 00:03:09,310
Take her away.

59
00:03:09,310 --> 00:03:10,240
Insolent!

60
00:03:10,470 --> 00:03:11,470
Let's see who dares.

61
00:03:12,240 --> 00:03:13,150
Guards.

62
00:03:13,400 --> 00:03:14,750
Stop her. Now.

63
00:03:16,000 --> 00:03:17,000
Concubine Hui.

64
00:03:17,000 --> 00:03:19,190
I'm ordered to protect you
by His Majesty.

65
00:03:19,630 --> 00:03:22,710
Others are not my responsibility.

66
00:03:22,840 --> 00:03:24,240
(I can't get out of this.)

67
00:03:24,360 --> 00:03:25,750
(Zhi Hui may not be able to save me.)

68
00:03:26,630 --> 00:03:27,680
I'll go on my own.

69
00:03:28,430 --> 00:03:29,560
I'll go with you.

70
00:03:30,150 --> 00:03:30,990
Lead the way.

71
00:03:31,680 --> 00:03:32,520
Ye Jin.

72
00:03:34,250 --> 00:03:35,840
Send a message
to the 14th Prince for me.

73
00:04:01,560 --> 00:04:03,190
Greetings, Your Ladyship.

74
00:04:03,630 --> 00:04:06,360
I heard you want my pastries.

75
00:04:06,800 --> 00:04:07,870
I'll make them now.

76
00:04:14,630 --> 00:04:15,800
Pastries?

77
00:04:18,600 --> 00:04:20,630
You think I called you here

78
00:04:20,950 --> 00:04:22,870
just for food?

79
00:04:25,560 --> 00:04:28,310
The moment
you chose to help Concubine Hui,

80
00:04:28,390 --> 00:04:31,000
you should've expected today's fate.

81
00:04:31,600 --> 00:04:33,440
I can't touch Concubine Hui,

82
00:04:33,750 --> 00:04:38,510
but killing you
is easier than killing a dog.

83
00:04:39,560 --> 00:04:40,400
Guards.

84
00:04:40,950 --> 00:04:43,390
Beat this lowly maid to death!

85
00:04:44,830 --> 00:04:45,750
Who dares to touch me?

86
00:04:46,950 --> 00:04:48,190
I belong to the Cining Palace.

87
00:04:48,240 --> 00:04:49,240
If you want to punish me,

88
00:04:49,260 --> 00:04:50,360
report to the Empress Dowager.

89
00:04:54,430 --> 00:04:55,430
The Empress Dowager?

90
00:04:56,430 --> 00:04:59,630
I curried favor for
the Empress's position for years.

91
00:05:00,430 --> 00:05:02,630
But now I see clearly.

92
00:05:03,190 --> 00:05:06,560
That position was never meant for me.

93
00:05:06,830 --> 00:05:10,390
So why should I hold back anymore?

94
00:05:11,190 --> 00:05:12,430
Do it.

95
00:05:16,920 --> 00:05:17,950
Let go of me!

96
00:05:29,480 --> 00:05:30,390
Your Ladyship.

97
00:05:30,560 --> 00:05:33,680
Since Ye Jin says the 14th Prince
can save her,

98
00:05:34,000 --> 00:05:35,630
we just need to send a letter.

99
00:05:35,950 --> 00:05:37,190
Why are you so worried?

100
00:05:37,750 --> 00:05:39,830
No. We can't tell him.

101
00:05:40,600 --> 00:05:42,120
He's only a Prince.

102
00:05:42,140 --> 00:05:43,750
He has no right to interfere
in harem affairs.

103
00:05:44,160 --> 00:05:45,560
If he steps in rashly,

104
00:05:45,560 --> 00:05:47,040
it'll just give others ammunition.

105
00:05:47,550 --> 00:05:48,560
We must tell His Majesty.

106
00:05:49,000 --> 00:05:51,630
But His Majesty is at the suburban camp.

107
00:05:52,190 --> 00:05:53,600
And he never liked Ye Jin.

108
00:05:54,000 --> 00:05:55,390
He may not be willing to deal with this.

109
00:05:56,240 --> 00:05:57,720
So I must find a way.

110
00:05:58,430 --> 00:06:00,310
A way that forces him to come back

111
00:06:00,630 --> 00:06:02,120
and see me.

112
00:06:02,120 --> 00:06:04,940
(Ningshou Palace)

113
00:06:10,720 --> 00:06:11,680
Let me go!

114
00:06:13,040 --> 00:06:14,070
Your Ladyship,

115
00:06:14,190 --> 00:06:16,680
you've been favored for years
but have no children.

116
00:06:16,920 --> 00:06:18,680
Have you never wondered why?

117
00:06:18,830 --> 00:06:19,670
Let go!

118
00:06:22,000 --> 00:06:23,000
Stop.

119
00:06:35,630 --> 00:06:36,750
You...

120
00:06:37,720 --> 00:06:39,190
What do you know?

121
00:06:39,830 --> 00:06:40,870
I know

122
00:06:41,210 --> 00:06:43,040
when Your Ladyship
first entered the palace,

123
00:06:45,680 --> 00:06:47,920
His Majesty loved your skin most.

124
00:06:48,310 --> 00:06:50,000
He praised your smooth, delicate skin.

125
00:06:50,240 --> 00:06:51,190
From then on,

126
00:06:51,190 --> 00:06:54,680
Your Ladyship cared more
about skincare than ever.

127
00:06:56,310 --> 00:06:58,630
Later, an Imperial Physician
catered to you

128
00:06:59,000 --> 00:07:01,680
and gave you a sweet drink
called White Dew.

129
00:07:02,310 --> 00:07:05,160
Since then,
Your Ladyship drank it every day.

130
00:07:05,510 --> 00:07:06,350
Am I right?

131
00:07:08,240 --> 00:07:09,310
This White Dew

132
00:07:09,600 --> 00:07:10,750
is an anti-fertility soup.

133
00:07:13,270 --> 00:07:14,270
Nonsense!

134
00:07:14,680 --> 00:07:18,070
Your Ladyship,
your family has many children.

135
00:07:18,430 --> 00:07:21,040
All five of your sisters
have sons and daughters.

136
00:07:21,630 --> 00:07:24,750
Yet you alone, favored for years,
have borne none.

137
00:07:24,900 --> 00:07:27,240
But the Imperial Physician said
you were well in every way.

138
00:07:28,040 --> 00:07:29,310
Except for this White Dew,

139
00:07:29,830 --> 00:07:31,480
what else can you think of?

140
00:07:35,830 --> 00:07:38,600
Your Ladyship,
Concubine Hui asks to see you urgently.

141
00:07:39,390 --> 00:07:40,230
Well?

142
00:07:40,560 --> 00:07:41,560
Is she giving birth?

143
00:07:42,830 --> 00:07:45,000
The Empress Dowager
and His Majesty value her most.

144
00:07:45,240 --> 00:07:47,310
She has dozens of servants.

145
00:07:48,000 --> 00:07:50,390
Midwives and nannies are all ready.

146
00:07:51,000 --> 00:07:53,240
I oversee the harem now,

147
00:07:54,310 --> 00:07:55,510
but I can't interfere

148
00:07:56,240 --> 00:07:58,510
in anything at her palace.

149
00:07:59,070 --> 00:08:00,830
She's here for Ye Jin.

150
00:08:01,360 --> 00:08:02,510
She says

151
00:08:02,510 --> 00:08:05,040
Consort Lan suddenly sent men
to seize Ye Jin.

152
00:08:05,360 --> 00:08:07,270
She wants me to save Ye Jin?

153
00:08:09,240 --> 00:08:10,870
Does she want to save her

154
00:08:10,870 --> 00:08:12,270
or get her killed faster?

155
00:08:13,270 --> 00:08:14,480
Interesting.

156
00:08:19,300 --> 00:08:20,310
What are you getting at?

157
00:08:20,630 --> 00:08:22,870
Why not let her come in first and talk?

158
00:08:23,390 --> 00:08:24,310
If people see her

159
00:08:24,310 --> 00:08:25,830
standing outside our palace,

160
00:08:26,120 --> 00:08:27,680
they'll think we're bullying her.

161
00:08:27,800 --> 00:08:28,920
After she came in, and then?

162
00:08:29,720 --> 00:08:30,720
She's heavily pregnant.

163
00:08:30,720 --> 00:08:32,000
If anything happens to her,

164
00:08:33,000 --> 00:08:35,670
I'll never explain it away.

165
00:08:36,480 --> 00:08:37,910
She's only an Imperial Physician.

166
00:08:38,840 --> 00:08:40,510
How dare she do this?

167
00:08:40,510 --> 00:08:42,200
You're so wise, Your Ladyship.

168
00:08:42,670 --> 00:08:44,360
You saw the key point at once.

169
00:08:46,510 --> 00:08:48,200
It was the Empress Dowager?

170
00:08:48,510 --> 00:08:49,350
No.

171
00:08:50,670 --> 00:08:51,790
It was His Majesty.

172
00:09:09,000 --> 00:09:10,000
You...

173
00:09:11,320 --> 00:09:13,630
are so good at making jokes.

174
00:09:16,270 --> 00:09:17,630
Joking or not.

175
00:09:18,290 --> 00:09:19,790
Your Ladyship knows it in your heart.

176
00:09:20,120 --> 00:09:21,840
His Majesty
fears your father and brother.

177
00:09:21,840 --> 00:09:23,510
How could he let you have a prince?

178
00:09:26,630 --> 00:09:28,870
Ye Jin, stop sowing discord!

179
00:09:29,270 --> 00:09:31,320
Everything you said is pure conjecture.

180
00:09:31,670 --> 00:09:33,840
Consort Lan drinks White Dew every day.

181
00:09:34,030 --> 00:09:36,240
If it's an anti-fertility soup as you say,

182
00:09:36,440 --> 00:09:37,910
how could Consort Lan be pregnant?

183
00:09:38,270 --> 00:09:40,320
That is the second secret I'll speak of.

184
00:09:40,720 --> 00:09:42,080
It's about that baby.

185
00:09:42,720 --> 00:09:45,200
Your Ladyship,
don't listen to her wild talk!

186
00:09:45,320 --> 00:09:46,870
Drag her out and beat her

187
00:09:47,320 --> 00:09:48,720
before she causes more trouble!

188
00:09:49,240 --> 00:09:51,200
Your Ladyship
has drunk White Dew for years,

189
00:09:51,240 --> 00:09:52,480
so you can't be pregnant.

190
00:09:52,720 --> 00:09:54,120
The current pregnancy signs

191
00:09:54,510 --> 00:09:56,910
are the effect of
the fake pregnancy drug.

192
00:09:59,150 --> 00:10:00,000
Nonsense.

193
00:10:00,000 --> 00:10:02,200
Your Ladyship takes a medicine
every morning at Chen hour,

194
00:10:02,200 --> 00:10:03,440
or the pregnancy signs will falter.

195
00:10:03,910 --> 00:10:04,750
Am I right?

196
00:10:05,390 --> 00:10:06,390
This pill is poisonous.

197
00:10:07,080 --> 00:10:08,120
If you skip one day,

198
00:10:08,320 --> 00:10:10,080
Your Ladyship will
feel worse than death.

199
00:10:11,520 --> 00:10:13,150
The one
who gave Your Ladyship this medicine

200
00:10:13,630 --> 00:10:14,960
hates you

201
00:10:15,320 --> 00:10:16,870
deeply.

202
00:10:20,870 --> 00:10:23,240
Your Ladyship, don't heed her wild talk!

203
00:10:23,510 --> 00:10:24,840
Is it nonsense or not?

204
00:10:24,910 --> 00:10:26,080
One try, and we'll know.

205
00:10:26,410 --> 00:10:28,440
Skip the medicine for one day,
and we'll know the truth.

206
00:10:30,000 --> 00:10:31,030
This medicine...

207
00:10:32,080 --> 00:10:33,630
I stopped taking it long ago.

208
00:10:35,200 --> 00:10:36,630
Just as she said,

209
00:10:36,720 --> 00:10:38,000
this pregnancy came strangely.

210
00:10:38,440 --> 00:10:40,910
I invited a famous physician
from outside.

211
00:10:40,910 --> 00:10:43,720
He saw the prescription was wrong
at once.

212
00:10:44,320 --> 00:10:45,160
Yunxi.

213
00:10:46,080 --> 00:10:50,150
Do you know why I called you here today?

214
00:10:51,720 --> 00:10:52,560
I...

215
00:10:59,720 --> 00:11:01,000
Today,

216
00:11:01,480 --> 00:11:03,600
the weather is clear.

217
00:11:04,080 --> 00:11:06,440
Perfect for killing.

218
00:11:07,720 --> 00:11:08,670
Guards!

219
00:11:09,150 --> 00:11:10,120
Seize her!

220
00:11:11,510 --> 00:11:13,080
Your Ladyship, don't listen to her!

221
00:11:13,080 --> 00:11:14,630
Your Ladyship, don't heed her nonsense!

222
00:11:15,000 --> 00:11:15,870
Your Ladyship!

223
00:11:16,200 --> 00:11:17,240
I have something urgent.

224
00:11:17,240 --> 00:11:18,600
I beg an audience with Consort De.

225
00:11:18,600 --> 00:11:20,080
Please let me in.

226
00:11:24,390 --> 00:11:25,270
Your Ladyship.

227
00:11:25,440 --> 00:11:26,790
Let's go back for now.

228
00:11:27,150 --> 00:11:29,000
Since Consort De won't lend a hand,

229
00:11:29,270 --> 00:11:30,390
we'll find another way.

230
00:11:30,600 --> 00:11:32,790
Your Ladyship, your health comes first.

231
00:11:32,960 --> 00:11:35,000
Please return to the palace and rest.

232
00:11:36,200 --> 00:11:37,390
Your Ladyship!

233
00:11:38,670 --> 00:11:40,670
His Majesty ordered you
to oversee the harem.

234
00:11:41,270 --> 00:11:44,030
So you should handle all harem affairs.

235
00:11:44,600 --> 00:11:46,840
Now Ye Jin is on the verge of death,

236
00:11:46,870 --> 00:11:48,080
yet you refuse to come out.

237
00:11:48,080 --> 00:11:49,480
How does that make sense?

238
00:11:51,750 --> 00:11:52,600
Your Ladyship.

239
00:11:56,750 --> 00:11:58,390
If Your Ladyship

240
00:11:59,870 --> 00:12:00,840
ignores this

241
00:12:01,750 --> 00:12:03,240
out of old grudges

242
00:12:03,390 --> 00:12:04,960
and refuses to help,

243
00:12:07,550 --> 00:12:08,550
I...

244
00:12:12,840 --> 00:12:15,000
I beg you, Your Ladyship.

245
00:12:15,670 --> 00:12:18,840
Please save Ye Jin, Your Ladyship.

246
00:12:23,360 --> 00:12:24,750
Any more secrets?

247
00:12:27,030 --> 00:12:27,870
Yes.

248
00:12:28,030 --> 00:12:28,870
And...

249
00:12:31,750 --> 00:12:33,600
Save them for the underworld.

250
00:12:36,630 --> 00:12:38,720
I'm tired today.

251
00:12:39,550 --> 00:12:41,220
I don't want to hear anymore.

252
00:12:45,030 --> 00:12:46,240
Do it.

253
00:12:51,360 --> 00:12:52,550
Your Ladyship!

254
00:12:53,200 --> 00:12:56,080
Please, for my sake,

255
00:12:56,600 --> 00:12:58,440
save Ye Jin!

256
00:12:58,670 --> 00:13:00,870
Your Ladyship, why must it be so?

257
00:13:01,000 --> 00:13:02,390
Your Ladyship, let's go back.

258
00:13:02,390 --> 00:13:03,230
Your Ladyship...

259
00:13:03,630 --> 00:13:07,320
Your Ladyship, please save Ye Jin.

260
00:13:09,510 --> 00:13:10,550
Consort Lan!

261
00:13:10,630 --> 00:13:12,240
I belong to the Cining Palace!

262
00:13:12,440 --> 00:13:14,150
How dare you treat me like this?

263
00:13:14,670 --> 00:13:15,510
Consort Lan!

264
00:13:16,390 --> 00:13:17,550
Let go of me!

265
00:13:18,840 --> 00:13:20,030
Let go of me!

266
00:13:21,630 --> 00:13:23,270
Let's go back, Your Ladyship.

267
00:13:28,440 --> 00:13:30,240
Please, Your Ladyship.

268
00:13:31,120 --> 00:13:33,080
Please save Ye Jin.

269
00:13:34,030 --> 00:13:35,240
Your Ladyship.

270
00:13:36,600 --> 00:13:37,440
Your Ladyship.

271
00:13:38,080 --> 00:13:38,920
Your Ladyship!

272
00:13:49,960 --> 00:13:52,600
I know everyone's ending,

273
00:13:52,750 --> 00:13:55,030
except my own.

274
00:13:57,480 --> 00:13:58,910
Maybe if I die like this,

275
00:13:59,390 --> 00:14:01,750
I can return to the real world.

276
00:14:02,480 --> 00:14:03,870
It hurts so much.

277
00:14:04,790 --> 00:14:05,630
Your Highness.

278
00:14:07,150 --> 00:14:08,080
Goodbye.

279
00:14:09,620 --> 00:14:10,460
Your Ladyship.

280
00:14:10,480 --> 00:14:11,330
Please...

281
00:14:11,360 --> 00:14:12,200
Your Ladyship!

282
00:14:13,390 --> 00:14:14,230
Your Ladyship!

283
00:14:14,240 --> 00:14:15,080
Your Ladyship!

284
00:14:15,550 --> 00:14:16,390
Please...

285
00:14:16,440 --> 00:14:17,280
Your Ladyship!

286
00:14:17,470 --> 00:14:18,320
Your Ladyship!

287
00:14:18,320 --> 00:14:19,240
Your Ladyship, let's return.

288
00:14:19,240 --> 00:14:20,080
Your Ladyship.

289
00:14:24,300 --> 00:14:25,670
- Please...
- Your Ladyship.

290
00:14:26,240 --> 00:14:27,240
- Please...
- Your Ladyship!

291
00:14:28,050 --> 00:14:29,040
- Please...
- Your Ladyship.

292
00:14:30,720 --> 00:14:31,600
Your Ladyship!

293
00:14:31,750 --> 00:14:32,630
Your Ladyship!

294
00:14:39,360 --> 00:14:40,240
Stop!

295
00:14:55,030 --> 00:14:55,870
What?

296
00:14:56,790 --> 00:14:58,030
You want to save her?

297
00:14:58,840 --> 00:15:03,000
No one I want dead
leaves this palace alive.

298
00:15:05,000 --> 00:15:05,840
No!

299
00:15:16,790 --> 00:15:17,630
Ye Jin!

300
00:15:22,000 --> 00:15:23,440
I'm sorry I'm late.

301
00:15:35,870 --> 00:15:37,870
His Majesty is here.

302
00:15:41,600 --> 00:15:42,750
Stop, 14th Prince!

303
00:15:43,870 --> 00:15:46,960
No one can stop me today!

304
00:15:47,240 --> 00:15:49,840
You want to kill me and die with her?

305
00:15:50,150 --> 00:15:51,150
Come on!

306
00:15:53,400 --> 00:15:54,480
Ye Jin is bleeding heavily.

307
00:15:54,480 --> 00:15:56,360
Are you going to
watch her die in front of you?

308
00:15:57,240 --> 00:15:58,670
Summon the Physician
to Cining Palace now!

309
00:15:59,200 --> 00:16:01,600
I'll give you an answer for today.

310
00:16:04,260 --> 00:16:05,120
Ye Jin.

311
00:16:05,120 --> 00:16:06,150
Let's go.

312
00:16:17,670 --> 00:16:19,360
Consort Lan is seriously ill.

313
00:16:20,030 --> 00:16:22,480
From today on, she is confined
to her palace to recover!

314
00:16:25,840 --> 00:16:27,240
Recover?

315
00:16:27,550 --> 00:16:29,670
I'm not ill!

316
00:16:31,030 --> 00:16:32,630
You're all ill.

317
00:16:33,440 --> 00:16:35,360
All of you!

318
00:16:36,440 --> 00:16:38,000
You're insane.

319
00:16:38,200 --> 00:16:39,390
Take her into custody!

320
00:16:44,390 --> 00:16:45,720
Your Majesty, bad news!

321
00:16:45,870 --> 00:16:47,240
Consort Hui is bleeding!

322
00:16:56,000 --> 00:16:58,440
♪I am but an outsider♪

323
00:16:58,480 --> 00:17:00,640
♪Yet something drags me deeper♪

324
00:17:00,880 --> 00:17:04,920
♪Outwit the world
but not the way we meet♪

325
00:17:04,920 --> 00:17:09,160
♪Splendid blooms line deadly ground♪

326
00:17:13,440 --> 00:17:16,680
♪Life's a phantom, yet I find you♪

327
00:17:16,840 --> 00:17:20,240
♪In a world of lies,
you're all that's clear♪

328
00:17:20,240 --> 00:17:22,760
♪I know how this story ends♪

329
00:17:22,760 --> 00:17:27,320
♪I still want what's in your eyes♪

330
00:17:27,640 --> 00:17:31,760
♪Truth or lie—I can't tell♪

331
00:17:36,720 --> 00:17:40,040
♪You hide it all behind your lines♪

332
00:17:40,040 --> 00:17:43,320
♪So familiar, yet out of reach♪

333
00:17:43,520 --> 00:17:46,600
♪A history that no one can search♪

334
00:17:46,840 --> 00:17:50,120
♪Like you drift in from another star♪

335
00:17:50,160 --> 00:17:51,920
♪I am but an outsider♪

336
00:17:51,920 --> 00:17:54,160
♪Yet something drags me deeper♪

337
00:17:54,160 --> 00:17:58,200
♪Outwit the world
but not the way we meet♪

338
00:17:58,200 --> 00:18:02,880
♪Splendid blooms line deadly ground♪

339
00:18:06,800 --> 00:18:10,200
♪Life's a phantom, yet I find you♪

340
00:18:10,200 --> 00:18:13,560
♪In a world of lies,
you're all that's clear♪

341
00:18:13,560 --> 00:18:16,040
♪I know how this story ends♪

342
00:18:16,040 --> 00:18:20,200
♪I still want what's in your eyes♪

343
00:18:20,200 --> 00:18:23,480
♪When it's over and I'm gone♪

344
00:18:23,480 --> 00:18:27,280
♪Please forget me and move on♪

345
00:18:27,280 --> 00:18:33,520
♪Just let this absurd dream fade♪

346
00:18:36,680 --> 00:18:45,040
♪Snow hides our tracks♪

347
00:18:48,600 --> 00:18:58,320
♪When do I finally wake♪
